#!/bin/sh 

SESSION=$(printf "Shutdown\\nReboot\\nLock\\nExit" | bemenu -H '20' -p 'Session:' --fn '$menufont' --tf '#ffffff' --hf '#000000' --hb '#999999') 

case $SESSION in 
	"Shutdown") doas shutdown -h now;; 
	"Reboot") doas shutdown -r now;;
	"Lock") slock;;
	"Exit") xdotool key "super+shift+e";; 
	*) ;; 
esac
